                <div style="text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary);">üìà Dashboard Anal√≠tico</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Visualize m√©tricas importantes e insights dos seus projetos em uma experi√™ncia completa</p>

                    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05) 0%, rgba(248, 250, 252, 1) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 600px;">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary);">üéØ Dashboards Dispon√≠veis</h3>
                        <div style="text-align: left; margin: 1rem 0;">
